Package: SGAT
Type: Package
Title: Solar/Satellite Geolocation for Animal Tracking
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Simon", "Wotherspoon", email = "Simon.Wotherspoon@utas.edu.au", role = "aut"),
    person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Simeon", "Lisovski", role = "aut"))
Description: Facilities for estimating the broadscale animal motions from
    archival or satellite tags. Locations are estimated using extensions of the 
    threshold, curve and satellite models of Sumner, Wotherspoon and Hindell (2009) 
    <http://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0007324> and Lisovski and Hahn (2012) 
    <http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.2041-210X.2012.00248.x/abstract>. 
Depends:
    R(>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    utils,
    MASS,
    maptools,
    raster,
    sp,
    coda
Suggests:
    GeoLight,
    geosphere,
    rgdal
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: no
ByteCompile: yes
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
